```plantuml
@startuml IBM_logdna-cos

actor User

participant "IBM COS" as COS
participant "Serverless Function" as Function
participant "LogDNA" as LogDNA
participant "COS Archive" as Archive

User -> COS: Upload log file
COS -> Function: New object creation event
Function -> COS: Download zipped log file
Function -> Function: Unzip and parse log data
alt Log size <= 10MB
    Function -> LogDNA: Send logs
else
    loop Batch logs (5000 each)
        Function -> LogDNA: Send logs
    end
end
Function -> Archive: Copy processed log file
Function -> COS: Delete processed log file

@enduml
```